---
title: Balsamic-Glazed Beef Rump with Orange & Green Bean Salad
description: Elevate your dinner game with this superquick gourmet meal! Juicy, tender beef is perfectly caramelised in a tangy-sweet balsamic glaze, then paired with a refreshing orange and green bean salad that’s bursting with citrusy crunch. It’s a bold and balanced dish that’s equal parts fancy and fun—sure to impress your taste buds!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

*We’ve replaced the pea pods in this recipe with green beans due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just
follow your recipe card!*
